      <p style="text-align:left;margin-left:-0in;margin-right:0in;text-indent:-0.01in"><docTitle style="font-weight:bold">IN THE MATTER OF THE MENTAL CAPACITY ACT 2005 </docTitle></p>
      <p style="text-align:right;margin-left:0.01in;margin-right:0.03in;text-indent:-0.01in"><span style="font-weight:bold">[2016] EWCOP 11 </span></p>
      <p style="text-align:right;margin-left:0.01in;margin-right:0.03in;text-indent:-0.01in"><span style="font-weight:bold">Royal Courts of Justice </span></p>
